title: O'Neill Girls wanna have fun
description: O'Neill Surfer girls, Amandine Sanchez and Alizé Arnaud, tell us about surfing, having fun and enjoying life... Girlz surfing is not only about bikinis and sexy attitude, it is also about shredding, commitment and writing your own story on waves...
